  "texts": [
    "AI polling exacerbates some of the ethical dilemmas present in traditional opinion polling.",
    "To understand the nature of the ethical challenges posed by AI polling, let us first turn back to traditional polling methods and their technical shortcomings.",
    "Traditional polling practices are based on sampling theory.",
    "You can think of sampling theory as a set of rules to generalise findings from a sample to the whole population of interest.",
    "For example, suppose you field a survey and ask the question: \"If the election for President of the United States were being held today, and the candidates were Donald Trump for the Republicans and Joe Biden for the Democrats, who would you vote for?\""
  ],
